<h1>Izubuchiâ€™s version of Eva, and the question of just how many eyes should be there</h1>
<p>â€” Actually Iâ€™ve heard that Mr.Â Izubuchi also took part in the designing of <em>Neon Genesis Evangelion</em> at that time, and I want to know about the story.</p>
